'''XEW-TV''' (channel 2 analog and channel 48 digital HDTV) is the [[call sign]] assigned to channel 2, a [[television station]] in [[Mexico City]], [[Mexico]]. The station is owned by [[Televisa]] and is the flagship station to the [[Canal de las Estrellas]] network. XEW is second oldest Televisa and Mexico City's station, founded in 1951.
